  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/39998952/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u39998952-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="陋巷瓢饮居士" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/39998952/">陋巷瓢饮居士</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:王家范</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/26379453/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u26379453-53.jpg" class="pil" alt="笑望江湖" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/26379453/">笑望江湖</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:历史 中国历史</span><br />

          <span class="">王家范确实是被忽略的一代史学大师，文笔洒脱酣畅，旁征博引不拘一格，极擅长从不为人知的史料细节中总结惊人的历史真相，剖析中国古代皇权与官僚黑暗体制的洞察力惊人，尤其是第6章格外精彩，如今的商界人士也需细读三思。缺点是太过侧重经济史与农业史，学术性过强，对非专业读者来说略显枯燥深奥</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/75704335/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u75704335-6.jpg" class="pil" alt="tomato熊吉君" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/75704335/">tomato熊吉君</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月20日          想读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
